<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>FiveM Status Page</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://wiki.fivem.net/w/images/thumb/f/f7/FiveMblack.png/300px-FiveMblack.png">
    <script src="jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
    <script>
      let seconds = 5
      setInterval(() => {
        if (seconds === 0) window.location = 'https://status.fivem.net/'
        seconds -= 1
        $('#seconds').html(seconds)
      }, 1000)
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="app">
        <h1 class="header">FiveM Status Page</h1>
        <h2>Hey! This website has been discontinued due to the creation of a official FiveM status page. You can check it out here: <a href="https://status.cfx.re/" style="color: #3ea4dc">https://status.fivem.net/</a></h2>
        <p>Sorry for leaving this online (and not working) for a while lol</p>
        <p>In case you have any questions I'll gladly answer them (IM NOT FROM THE FIVEM TEAM OK???) My discord is Bee#1111 just in case</p>
        <p>Redirecting you to the official website in <span id="seconds">5</span> seconds...</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- This should probably be in a separate file, but meh. -->
    <style>
      p {
        margin: 0
      }

      body {
        height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        background-color: #333;
        color: #bbb;
      }

      .statuses {
        padding-bottom: 0.5em;
      }

      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .app {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header {
        color: #ddd;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .footer {
        color: #666;
      }

      .link {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .unrelatedNote {
        font-size: 10px;
      }

    </style>
  </body>
</html>
